{"tid":1714620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解林鄭死都唔肯宣布停工停課？","createTime":"2019-11-13T02:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:27:21.000Z","uid":37656,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"07acd784a598ac4dc7c75280f0bf49f27cc23fc9","tid":1714620,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:09:37.000Z","msg":"因為佢知道停工停課大家就唔再需要藉口，直接出晒街全民抗爭，佢就收硬皮"},{"pid":"22e2ce695a2a120e5122f0d7ef8db07acfbace37","tid":1714620,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a><br />\n<br />\n再接再厲"},{"pid":"4a6cc88853d408a8c898265faf8644eb1522fc23","tid":1714620,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:12:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"c3a5c5a4095aeef2836da06a03eaf6757fc72f34","tid":1714620,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"返學成功地鐵巴士封晒放學點走呀 成班垃圾高官用屎忽諗野"},{"pid":"626d46810a926a6256d7cc3b300d465bf4cd423c","tid":1714620,"uid":37656,"like"